title: Did viral images show that people were climbing a border fence that Trump said: " Can't climb '?
subtitle: The social media used some old images from different locations to challenge the President ' s bragging about a new model of the border fence.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: The widely shared images in September 2019 showed that people easily climbed the same fence, or the same kind of fence, that United States President Donald Trump said "can't climb."
